  <slide>
    <title>Issues in IT Accessibility</title>
    <contents>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Human resources</strong>: There are not enough people who undestand the experience of disability and the technqiues to make resources more accessible.</li>
        <li><strong>Roles</strong>: No one needs to know everything, but everyone needs to know something to contribute to accessibility.</li>
        <li><strong>Authoring</strong>: Authoring tools need to support accessibility by default, rather than by exception.</li>
        <li><strong>Standards</strong>: Standards need to support accessibility and provide a means to make it easier to make resources more accessible.</li>
      </ul>
    </contents>
